Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.patterns.ui.behaviors.searchSuggest

Interface Summary
SearchSuggestGroup A Grouping of Search Suggest items as shown in the Global Search field in Fusion Apps.
 

Class Summary
AbstractSearchSuggestGroup A Grouping of Search suggest items as shown below an inputText field in Fusion Apps.
BackgroundSearchSuggestRunnable A runnable for running init() on SearchSuggestGroups in a background thread.
FavoriteItemsSearchSuggestGroup A Search Suggest Group for applcore favorite items.
GlobalLastSearchSuggestGroup A Search Suggest Group for the last applcore Global Search Recent Search.
GlobalRecentSearchSuggestGroup A Search Suggest Group for applcore Global Search Recent Search names previously saved by the current user.
GlobalSavedSearchSuggestGroup A grouping of Global Search Saved Search names previously saved by the current user.
KeywordSearchSuggestGroup A grouping of search keywords previously submitted by the current user.
NavigatorMenuSearchSuggestGroup A grouping of navigator menu items available to the current user.
RecentItemsSearchSuggestGroup A Search Suggest Group for applcore recent items.
SearchSuggestItem An suggestion to be shown to the user in an an SearchSuggestGroup.
WatchlistSearchSuggestGroup An Autosuggest group based on ATK Watchlists.
 

Enum Summary
SearchSuggestGroup.GroupHeading Valid return values for the getGroupHeading() API.
SearchSuggestGroup.GroupIcon Valid values for the Group Icons.
